cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object detection in images, specifically paintings. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with a new database of iconographic elements in paintings. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of globally annotated databases for on-the-fly learning of new classes. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for weakly supervised object detection. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a multiple-instance learning method for object detection.
